snippet.title: World of Kings Gameplay Official Launch
snippet.description:
World of Kings will be officially released on 30. May. Pre-register right now and you still have the chances to get pre-registration rewards!
 
Official site: https://www.zloong.com/wwhd/?s=Y03
iOS Link: https://apple.co/2PbqRIF
Google Play Link: https://bit.ly/2Ug4wKZ
 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WorldofKingsEN/
Discord: https://discord.gg/KpAsHGT 
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/WorldofKings/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WorldofKings2
ins:https://www.instagram.com/world_of_kings2019/
